channel.title: My server is not running anymore(with pictures please help)
channel.description:
Oke My server has been running for 1 year and know my server worked 1 week ago and now it is not running anymore i tried it so many times. I got pictures to help you i got all the pictures what i have running for my server to work. Please if you see anything wrong tell me.
Because I tried everything all again it still doesnt work it's weird :|
[b]1: Java[/b] [img]http://img222.imageshack.us/img222/9338/ssbq5.png[/img] [b]2:Source[/b] [img]http://img526.imageshack.us/img526/5109/ssdgp1.png[/img] [b]3: No-ip[/b] [img]http://img526.imageshack.us/img526/4411/fdgsflp1.png[/img] [b]4: Portforwarding[/b] [img]http://img526.imageshack.us/img526/1653/sadassx9.png[/img] [b]5: Firewall exceptions[/b] [img]http://img526.imageshack.us/img526/1760/sdaakp7.png[/img] [b]6: System variables.[/b] [img]http://img526.imageshack.us/img526/3800/sadasdsafhy2.png[/img]

item.title: My server is not running anymore(with pictures please help)
item.dc:creator: @Noob.Coder Noob.Coder
item.description:
@Noob.Coder wrote:

update your java to the newest version
That is not the problem I have been running my server on JDK 5.0 and JRE 5.0, It's not the Java processes that's wrong, what most likely happened is your IP address changed so go to run and type in cmd then type ipconfig and update that to your portforward site. That happened to me once. I hope this helped you bud. Hope to see your server be a #1 hit.
